OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry throughout the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight. Some spells of evening
OL,8,Fsunshine but gradually turning hazier.
OL,9,FSome clear spells possible overnight,
OL,10,Fcloudier in the north.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FDry and warm with lengthy
OL,13,Fsunny spells for much of the day, but
OL,14,Fcloud spreads south in the evening
OL,15,Fwith the odd spot of light rain
OL,16,Fpossible in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
